---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Documentation" description="Learn how to use LinguAI for acoustic analysis">
  <h1>Documentation</h1>
  <p class="lead">
    Welcome to the LinguAI documentation. Learn how to use our AI-native acoustic analysis
    platform to streamline your phonetic research.
  </p>

  <div class="cards">
    <a href="/docs/getting-started" class="card">
      <h3>Getting Started</h3>
      <p>Install LinguAI and create your first project in under 5 minutes.</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/docs/spectrogram" class="card">
      <h3>Spectrogram Analysis</h3>
      <p>Learn how to view, analyze, and export spectrograms with precision.</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/docs/annotations" class="card">
      <h3>Annotations</h3>
      <p>Create, edit, and export annotations with AI assistance or manually.</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2>Quick Links</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/adtruiz/linguai/releases">Download the latest release</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/adtruiz/linguai">View the source code on GitHub</a></li>
    <li><a href="/blog">Read our blog for tips and tutorials</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Need Help?</h2>
  <p>
    If you can't find what you're looking for, feel free to:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/adtruiz/linguai/issues">Open an issue on GitHub</a></li>
    <li><a href="mailto:hello@linguai.app">Email us at hello@linguai.app</a></li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .card h3 {
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
</style>
